<p><strong>Item #:</strong> <a href="/scp-5583">SCP-5583</a></p>



<div class="scp-image-block block-right" style="width:175px;"><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/this-page-intentionally-left-blank/Skippy.png" title="Click and hold to enlarge." style="width:175px;" class="fillpg" alt="Skippy.png" />
<div class="scp-image-caption" style="width:175px;">
<p>My &quot;art&quot; without the background.</p>
